  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "\"Th\xE0nh H\xE1t-xo s\u1EBD tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh hang c\u1EE7a ch\xF3 r\u1EEBng; n\xF3 s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFn th\xE0nh sa m\u1EA1c hoang vu \u0111\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EDDi. S\u1EBD kh\xF4ng c\xF3 ai \u1EDF \u0111\xF3, kh\xF4ng ai tr\xFA trong th\xE0nh \u0111\xF3.\"L\u1EDDi ti\xEAn tri v\u1EC1 \xCA-lam "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v34"
  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "\xCDt l\xE2u sau khi X\xEA-\u0111\xEA-kia l\xEAn ng\xF4i vua Giu-\u0111a th\xEC CH\xDAA ph\xE1n c\xF9ng nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 l\u1EDDi ti\xEAn tri ngh\u1ECBch c\xF9ng d\xE2n \xCA-lam . "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v35"
  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng ph\xE1n: \"Ta s\u1EAFp b\u1EBB g\xE3y c\xE2y cung c\u1EE7a \xCA-lam, t\u1EE9c s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh v\xF4 song c\u1EE7a n\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD mang b\u1ED1n gi\xF3 ngh\u1ECBch l\u1EA1i \xCA-lam t\u1EEB b\u1ED1n g\xF3c tr\u1EDDi. Ta s\u1EBD ph\xE2n t\xE1n d\xE2n n\xF3 ra kh\u1EAFp b\u1ED1n h\u01B0\u1EDBng gi\xF3; t\xF9 binh n\xF3 s\u1EBD t\u1EA3n l\u1EA1c kh\u1EAFp c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn cho \xCA-lam ho\u1EA3ng s\u1EE3 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t k\u1EBB th\xF9 m\xECnh, l\xE0 nh\u1EEFng k\u1EBB mu\u1ED1n ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t ch\xFAng. Ta s\u1EBD mang th\u1EA3m h\u1ECDa \u0111\u1EBFn cho \xCA-lam \u0111\u1EC3 ch\u1EE9ng t\u1ECF c\u01A1n th\u1ECBnh n\u1ED9 ta!\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy. \"Ta s\u1EBD sai g\u01B0\u01A1m \u0111u\u1ED5i \xCA-lam cho \u0111\u1EBFn khi ta \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EBFt s\u1EA1ch ch\xFAng n\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v38"
  }, "v38"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD l\u1EADp ng\xF4i ta trong \xCA-lam \u0111\u1EC3 ch\u1EE9ng t\u1ECF ta l\xE0 vua, ta s\u1EBD ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t vua v\xE0 qu\u1EA7n th\u1EA7n n\xF3!\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v39"
  }, "v39"), mdx("p", null, "\"Nh\u01B0ng trong t\u01B0\u01A1ng lai ta s\u1EBD ph\u1EE5c h\u1ED3i \xCA-lam,\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
